import React, { useState } from "react"; import sellnowService, {addPerson} from "../services/sellnowService"; const SellNow = () => { const [brand, setBrand] = useState(``) const [processor, setProcessor] = useState(``) const [productType, setProductType] = useState(``) const [generation, setGeneration] = useState(``) const [touchscreen, setTouchscreen] = useState(``) const [screen, setScreen] = useState(``) const [graphics, setGraphics] = useState(``) const [ram, setRAM] = useState(``) const [hdd, setHDD] = useState(``) const [ssd, setSSD] = useState(``) const [file, setFile] = useState(null); const [status, setStatus] = useState(""); const handleFileUpload = (event) => { setFile(event.target.files[0]); }; const handleSubmit = (event) => { event.preventDefault(); const newPerson = { brand:brand, processor: processor, productType: productType, generation: generation, touchscreen: touchscreen, screenSize:screen, graphics:graphics, ram:ram, hddCapacity:hdd, ssdCapacity:ssd, maritalStatus: status, }; if ( status !== "") { sellnowService.addPerson(newPerson); setStatus(""); setBrand(""); setGeneration(""); setProductType(""); setTouchscreen(""); setScreen(""); setGraphics(""); setRAM(""); setHDD(""); setSSD(""); } }; return (
); }; let ssd = ''; function setSSDValue(value) { ssd = value; } export default SellNow;
